<div class="backlog-tool-panel">
  <% if (!model.CanEdit()) { %>
    <h2>Sprint read-only</h2>
    You do not have permission to edit any of the settings of this backlog's sprint.
  <% } else { %>
    <h2>Delete sprint</h2>
    <% if (model.IsComplete()) { %>
      This sprint is no longer editable as it is marked as complete.  If you need to delete this sprint, mark this sprint as incomplete.
    <% } else if (!model.get('deletable?')) { %>
      This sprint cannot be deleted as it is not the last sprint.  You must delete all successive sprints before you can delete this sprint.
    <% } else { %>
      Deleting a sprint immediately will remove all stories from this sprint and this sprint will be <b>permanently deleted</b>.
      <b>There is no undo</b> so make sure you absolutely sure you want to delete this sprint.
      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="#delete-sprint" class="delete-sprint">Yes, I understand â€” delete this sprint</a>
      </div>
    <% } %>
  <% } %>
</div>